      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. ODIN (1) was in the money last time out when third and beaten 4.5 lengths at Warragul over 460m (26.48). Has failed to finish in the placings from two starts here. Form from his last run is proving strong. Likely to feature again. DR. MONICA (3) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.3 lengths at Sale in a handy 24.91 beating Hurry Dusty. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. SWEET TRILBY (7) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including two wins. Below best last time at Sale (24.65) in a Grade 5, finishing a 2.5 lengths fifth. Can feature with the right run. DR. DYLAN (8) is not to be discarded.",
